<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-404] Synpase is blocked and does not deliver responses</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-404</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After a while of normal operation Synapse does not deliver responses and seems to be blocked. Having a look at the threaddump of an instance in this state the client worker threads are waiting for a notifaction which is never send. This issue might be related to IOExceptions which occured before due to some client-side timeouts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please find attached a threaddump of an instance in this state. There you will also see an issue with duplicated threads which are probably a result of gracefuly restarts via JMX. Although both issues must not be related and could be handled separated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
